{"tid":345770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一樣你有既恐懼症","createTime":"2017-08-03T10:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T20:55:02.000Z","uid":81287,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"253d1b64cef75d7a9710276bdd779a136c44aeb7","tid":345770,"uid":81287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T10:59:48.000Z","msg":"我先<br />\n西瓜恐懼症<br />\n<br />\n細個唔知點解有段時間西瓜好撚平<br />\n老豆每隔一日都會買個返黎，自始唔再食西瓜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe7ddab4a1e808ae72b71ebc38417c2c4c67178d","tid":345770,"uid":81287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bcbddc150e0a3f7a18aba87cf8927f148c7ba8b","tid":345770,"uid":116330,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:01:58.000Z","msg":"香港"},{"pid":"a1515200d8a1cf69d026973772aa1c11c8704e1d","tid":345770,"uid":76038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:02:28.000Z","msg":"小強<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"650a2c2319044c055c162775c9543f5cc736f636","tid":345770,"uid":133042,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:03:58.000Z","msg":"人"},{"pid":"31d2b01bd841f9bd8d63385262524517b56712b0","tid":345770,"uid":113034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:04:05.000Z","msg":"密集<br />\n昆蟲<br />\n肥膩野食<br />\n係n樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5a81d0b8971c9d670a402d632d5e2c6fb115f3d","tid":345770,"uid":95237,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T11:04:12.000Z","msg":"扣肉恐懼症<br />\n<br />\n細個有一次食太多梅菜扣肉<br />\n食到腸胃炎入急症<br />\n幾年唔敢再食<br />\n大個左之後 每次只係敢食一舊"},{"pid":"78674c79a3a7ef118a77b9a3abdf1ee589cc4f7e","tid":345770,"uid":108356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":